{"word":"G4648 - σκοπέω - skopéō - skop-eh'-o - Consider","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σκοπέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>skopéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>skop-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Consider"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - எச்சரிக்கையாயிரு, நோக்கு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to look at, observe, contemplate, to mark"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G4649 - σκοπός - skopós - skop-os'/4649\">G4649</a>; to take <i>aim</i> at (<i>spy</i>), that is, (figuratively) <i>regard:</i> - consider, take heed, look at (on), mark. Compare <a href=\"#/G3700 - ὀπτάνομαι - optánomai - op-tan'-om-ahee/3700\">G3700</a>."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2684 - κατασκοπέω - kataskopéō - kat-as-kop-eh'-o/2684\">G2684</a>, <a href=\"#/G2685 - κατάσκοπος - katáskopos - kat-as'-kop-os/2685\">G2685</a>, <a href=\"#/G4648 - σκοπέω - skopéō - skop-eh'-o/4648\">G4648</a>, <a href=\"#/G4649 - σκοπός - skopós - skop-os'/4649\">G4649</a>"}]}